      "text": "输入说明\nreference_features\n形状：[R, B, 256]\n语义：多个参考框对应的 embedding\nreference_valid_mask\n形状：[R, B]\n语义：reference 是否有效\nreference_weight\n形状：[1]\n语义：reference 特征融合强度",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "输入说明\nreference_features\n形状：[R, B, 256]\n语义：多个参考框对应的 embedding\nreference_valid_mask\n形状：[R, B]\n语义：reference 是否有效\nreference_weight\n形状：[1]\n语义：reference 特征融合强度",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "XtgfIE_fB_fp-GkIeZ8zF",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 446.5696563020843,
      "y": 1433.8377326901268,
      "width": 514.3993530273438,
      "height": 120,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b6a",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 983419455,
      "version": 4,
      "versionNonce": 1536843423,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1775484468748,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "wrapper 内部大致逻辑是：\n根据 reference_valid_mask 过滤无效 reference\n对 reference_features 做有效项平均\n形成 reference_bias\n将 reference_weight * reference_bias 加到 language_features\n再执行普通 grounding decoder",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "wrapper 内部大致逻辑是：\n根据 reference_valid_mask 过滤无效 reference\n对 reference_features 做有效项平均\n形成 reference_bias\n将 reference_weight * reference_bias 加到 language_features\n再执行普通 grounding decoder",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
